Page 23 = Kto je kto? = Who is who? (Muz = Male vs Zena = female) :
Pan = Mr. Vs Pani(Dama) = Lady / Pan Vs Slecna = Miss / Chlapec = Boy vs Dievca = Girl / Brat = Brother vs Sestra = Sister / Splubyvajuci = Couple Vs Splubyvajuca = Couple / Kolega = Colleague vs Kolegyna = Colleague
priatel = Boyfriend vs priatelka = Girlfriend / ucitel vs ucitelka = Teacher / student vs studentka = Student / manazer vs manazerka = Manager  
  11: Doplnte = Supplement (fill in the ending of word) : profesorka / ministerka / prezidentka / sefka / lektorka
  12: Doplnte = Supplement (fill in the ending) : 
    Not Married male = Robert Soltys -> Robert je Slobodny = robert is single / Not Married Female = Johanna Mark -> johanna slobodna = Johanna is single 
    Married Male = Peter Vrana -> Peter je zenaty = peter is married + peter vrana je manzel = peter vrana is a husband
    Married Female = Eva Vranova -> Eva je vydata = Eva is married  + Pani vranova je manzelka = Eva is a wife
Page 24 = Personalne Pronomina = Personal Pronouns :
Male = Ends with 'y' / Female = Ends with 'a'
Singular Vs Plural : Ja Vs My / Ty vs Vy / on+ona+ono Vs Oni+Ony
