Page 42 = Posesive Adjektiva = Possesive Adjectives : Ci / Cia / Cie
  For Males(add to end of name) - Ci = ov (robertov) / Cia = ova (robertova) / Cie = ovo (Robertovo auto=Roberts car)
  For Females(add to end of name) - Ci = in (zuzanin) / Cia = Ina (zuzanina) / Cie = ino (zuzanino auto=Susanas Car)
